<TEXT>
GOLD shares remained firm on overseas interest and the index advanced
another 27 to 1,017, with Vaal Reefs gaining R10 at R190 and Southvaal up
R3.50 to R52.50. The industrial index fell 42 to 4,603 while the overall
index rose 10 to 3,551.
