<HEADLINE>
FT  11 FEB 93 / Fraud inquiry
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
POLICE are investigating an alleged fraud at the British Council, Scotland
Yard confirmed yesterday. The council is responsible for furthering British
trade and cultural interests abroad.
